                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270111-116-off642 t18270111-116-cd643"></join>, 2 gowns, value 1s. 6d.; 4 pairs of stockings, value 2s.; 1 handkerchief, value 1s.; 1 sheet, value 1s.; 1 quilt, value 1s.; 1 shift, value 6d.; 2 petticoats, value 1s.; 1 shirt, value 6d.; 1 frock, value 3d., and 3 pincloths, value 6d., the goods of 
                     
