                     <interp inst="t18270111-116-person1147" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . This shift and petticoat are mine. The prosecutrix had them to mangle.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270111-116-person1148">
                  DANIEL 
                  REARDON
               <interp inst="t18270111-116-person1148" type="surname" value="REARDON"></interp>
